<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Basic HTML</title>
</head>

<body>

    <h1>Welcome to My HTML Page</h1>

    <h2>Text Formatting</h2>

    <p>
        This is <b>bold</b> text. <br>
        This is <strong>important</strong> text. <br>
        This is <i>italic</i> text. <br>
        This is <em>emphasized</em> text. <br>
        This is <u>underlined</u> text. <br>
        This is <mark>highlighted</mark> text. <br>
        This is <small>smaller</small> text. <br>
        Water formula: H<sub>2</sub>O <br>
        Einstein's formula: E = mc<sup>2</sup> <br>

        Code:
        <code>
            &lt;h5&gt;Hi, this is written in "code" tag.&lt;/h5&gt;
        </code>
    </p>

    <h1>HTML Lists with Different Types</h1>

    <h2>Unordered Lists</h2>

    <h3>Default (disc)</h3>
    <ul type="disc">
        <li>Apple</li>
        <li>Banana</li>
        <li>Cherry</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Circle</h3>
    <ul type="circle">
        <li>Dog</li>
        <li>Cat</li>
        <li>Rabbit</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Square</h3>
    <ul type="square">
        <li>Red</li>
        <li>Green</li>
        <li>Blue</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Ordered Lists</h2>

    <h3>Numbers (1,2,3...)</h3>
    <ol type="1">
        <li>Python</li>
        <li>Java</li>
        <li>PHP</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Uppercase Letters (A,B,C...)</h3>
    <ol type="A">
        <li>HTML</li>
        <li>CSS</li>
        <li>JavaScript</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Lowercase Letters (a,b,c...)</h3>
    <ol type="a">
        <li>C++</li>
        <li>C#</li>
        <li>C</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Uppercase Roman (I,II,III...)</h3>
    <ol type="I">
        <li>MySQL</li>
        <li>MongoDB</li>
        <li>Firebase</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Lowercase Roman (i,ii,iii...)</h3>
    <ol type="i">
        <li>Dart</li>
        <li>R</li>
        <li>Kotlin</li>
    </ol>

    <hr>

    <h1 align="center">Welcome to My Webpage</h1>

    <h3>
        Below I have used anchor tag "a" for hyperlink. After clicking on the
        link you will be redirected to the Wikipedia page.
    </h3>

    <a href="https://www.wikipedia.org" target="_blank">
        Wikipedia
    </a>

    <h2>Images</h2>

    <p>Here are some images from the web:</p>

    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/61/HTML5_logo_and_wordmark.svg"
         alt="HTML5 Logo"
         width="200">

    <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6a/JavaScript-logo.png"
         alt="JavaScript Logo"
         width="200">

    <h2>Programming Languages Table</h2>

    <table border="1" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0">

        <tr>
            <th>Language</th>
            <th>Type</th>
            <th>Website</th>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>HTML</td>
            <td>Markup</td>
            <td>
                <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML" target="_blank">
                    Learn HTML
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>CSS</td>
            <td>Style Sheet</td>
            <td>
                <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS" target="_blank">
                    Learn CSS
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>JavaScript</td>
            <td>Programming</td>
            <td>
                <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript" target="_blank">
                    Learn JS
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>

    </table>

</body>
</html>
